{"word":"μαλακίζομαι","slug":"μαλακίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαλακίζομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μαλακός'><el>μαλακός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be softened</i> or <i>made effeminate, shew weakness</i> or <i>cowardice</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be softened</i> or <i>appeased</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}